* Changes in version 0.2.0 (2026-04-15)
** New =(pnm graphics)= module
This module contains some basic pixel manipulation for PNM images, namely:
- =pnm-image-pixel= allows to get a pixel value from an image.
- =pnm-image-pixel-set!= allows to set a pixel to a specified value in an
  image.
** =README.org=: Fix a typo and update
Fix a typo and add a command example for installing Guile-PNM from the GNU
Guix repository.
** =(pnm image)=
*** =pnm-image->pbm-binary-image=: Rename                        :API_CHANGE:
Rename =pnm-image->pbm-binary-image= to =pbm-ascii-image->pbm-binary-image=.
*** =pnm-image->pbm-ascii-image=: Rename                         :API_CHANGE:
Rename =pnm-image->pbm-ascii-image= to =pbm-binary-image->pbm-ascii-image=.
* Changes in version 0.1.0 (2026-04-13)
** Release of the first version of Guile-PNM

